node.text: You can be the 2021 @usaskateboarding Fingerboarding National Champion! Post up to a :45 second unedited fingerboarding video on Instagram and hashtag #usafbnc #usaskateboarding #techdeck by May 4th for your chance to be crowned the first ever United States Fingerboarding National Champion presented by Tech Deck – full details at USASkateboarding.com
